title.rendered: STEDI 10W MINI V2 LED FLOOD LIGHT

content.rendered:
What’s Included

  • 1 x 10W Mini V2 LED Flood Light
  • 2 x M6 Bolts
  • 1 x Nylock Nut + 1 x Standard Nut
  • 1 x Flat Washer + 1 x Lock Washer
  • Male & Female Deutsch Connectors

WITHOUT A SHADOW OF A DOUBT

Our 10w Mini LED Work Light packs a powerful punch for a small, 300g light; a big reason as to why it has become a fan favorite. We have taken the 10w Mini LED Work Light to the next level by incorporating a more secure set of fasteners into the lens. Without a shadow of a doubt, this new version has proven to be a solid and durable upgrade for your vehicle.

 

POWERFUL PERFORMANCE

Running a 2x5w Osram LEDs supplies more light than you would expect from a 300g light. With a 40 degree flood and a low current draw of 0.5a @ 13.8v, it really is no surprise that they are our best selling LED Work Light.

ENDLESS APPLICATION

The 10w Minis have a huge variety of applications and can be used from work/camping lights to bumper-mounted reverse lights. The 2 styles of 10w Mini are easily mounted via the U-Bracket or Flush Face Plate depending on the intended location of the light. We also have a 10w Mini LED Work Light available in a flush mount. If you’ve been trying to upgrade the dull, factory reverse lights, then these are the perfect option

DETAILS

KEY FEATURES

  • Flood Optics for a wide 40 degree spread pattern
  • 12 Volt and 24v Compatible
  • Waterproof Male & Female Deutsch connectors included
  • Stainless Steel Fittings
  • IP67 – Protected against immersion up to 1m in depth for no longer than 30 minutes at a time
  • OSRAM GmbH Emitters

Tech Specs

LED POWER 10 Watts
OPERATING VOLTAGE 12v & 24v Compatible
LED CHIPS 5W x 2 Osram LED’s
COLOUR TEMPERATURE 5700K
OPERATING TEMPERATURE -40°C to 60°C
RAW LUMENS 1,000Lm
CURRENT DRAW 0.5A @ 13.8V
BEAM Flood Beam
WATERPROOF IP67
DUSTPROOF & ANTI-VIBRATION Yes
LENS Optical PC
MOUNTING BRACKET Stainless Steel
HOUSING MATERIAL Cast Aluminum Housing
LIFE SPAN 50,000+ Hrs
DIMENSIONS (W x H x D) 77mm x 48mm x 55mm
CERTIFICATES CE, RoHs & ECE
WEIGHT 0.3kg
